A fitness instructor has been shot dead after a masked man walked up to him in a gym filled with people and fired his gun.

The man, identified by friends as gym owner Richard Millsap, was pronounced dead at the scene. 

The killer, identified as a black male, and an accomplice are still on the loose, following the fatal shooting at the CrossFit Mosaic Gym in Winter Garden, Florida on Monday.  

'Fatal shooting': Richard Millsap, owner of the Florida CrossFit, is believed to have been shot dead at his gym on Monday

